headline: YMX Logistics Hosts Webinar with Manufacturing Leaders on Enterprise Yard Operations
summary: YMX Logistics, a national leader in integrated yard logistics, is bringing together top supply chain leaders for an online event on October 14, 2025, at 1:00 PM EDT to talk about one of the most overlooked links in the manufacturing supply chain: yard operations. The session will explore how manufacturers are transforming yard operations into a connected performance lever.
